  [:li "To manage our networks;"]
  [:li "To protect the security or integrity of the App, our users, and of our business;"]
  [:li "To provide to third party providers that may fulfill products or services for which you have shown interest;"]
  [:li "As described to you at the point of data collection; and"]
  [:li "To use banking information (only to process payments and prevent fraud)*."]]
 [:p "We do not use your Proprietary in any capacity or Personally Identifiable Information for commercial advertisements or marketing material from us or third parties without your explicit consent or to opt-in or opt-out, with the default being set to opt-out."]
 [:p "We may use your personal information (excluding your proprietary or financial information) and your App usage information (such as anonymous user usage data, cookies, IP addresses, browser type, and other automatically recorded usage information) to improve the quality and design of the App and to create new features, promotions, functionality, and services by storing, tracking, and analyzing user preferences and trends."]
